# CLAUDE.md — {{PROJECT_NAME}}

## Project Overview
{{PROJECT_NAME}} is a full-stack web application deployed to the Duin Home homelab.

**Stack:** Next.js (frontend) + Express/Prisma (backend) + Supabase (auth) + Docker + Traefik

**URL:** https://{{PROJECT_NAME}}.duin.home

## Architecture
- **Frontend**: Next.js + Mantine UI + Zustand state management
- **Backend**: Express.js + Prisma ORM + Zod validation
- **Auth**: Supabase (JWT in httpOnly cookies)
- **Deploy**: Docker Compose via Portainer GitOps (push to main = deploy)

## Key Constraints
- **Never hardcode IPs** — use DNS names (*.duin.home)
- **Never restart containers directly** — push to main, Portainer auto-deploys
- **Always run `make check` before pushing**
- **All API inputs validated with Zod**
- **Prisma only** — no raw SQL
- **Tests target staging Supabase only** — never production
